<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90aa61db-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s6084"><num value="6084">§ 6084.</num><heading> Limitation of actions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">An action under <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s6082">section 6082 of this title</ref> may not be brought more than 2 years after the trafficking giving rise to the action has ceased to occur.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id90aa61dc-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/114/tIII/s305">Pub. L. 104–114, title III, § 305</ref>, <date date="1996-03-12">Mar. 12, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/821">110 Stat. 821</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
